item.description: For Server Hosting Cloud #hosting #server So What are we looking for in a web service provider? here’s what I’ll base them on- Design Process - How complex the work is and weather or not it has a UI Designer Integration - How much of a pain is it to set up your own services on it Community - How big and supportive the community is Here are the options .
